0.front: Welcome to FlashMemorize!! - - - double tap the screen to flip the card!
0.back: Great Job! Now you are on the back size of a card. - - - Swipe right or left to navigate through the deck!

1.front: You are now on the second card! - - - -You can also use buttons prev and next to navigate around. - - - Tap "Good" button if feel good about the card, and "Bad" if you feel bad about a card. Try it!

2.front: Good Job and welcome to the 3rd card! - - -FlashMemorize tracks your record of "Good" and "Bad" on each card. It comes in handy when you use Smart Shuffling. Tap the "menu" button on the top right corner and tap "Study Stats" to view your performance on each card! - - - There are more tips on the next card!

3.front: Welcome to the 4th card! You can view images using FlashMemorize. - -Long press on a picture to zoom in. - -For more guides, visit github.com/timchenggu123/FlashMemorizeDroid {example3.jpg}
3.back: You have reached the end XD!
